 Keep up with the restless undergrads – Uriel, Flex, Cassandra and Martins in episode four of B’Concept Network’s web series “Bad Gang”. “Bad Gang” follows the antics of five university undergraduates. It was directed and produced by Victor Opkala. The series features Shawn Faqua, Uche Nwaefuna, Deborah Anugwa, Becky Eloho, James Smart, Francis Onwuchie, Susan Pwajok, Stephen Damian and many others. Watch the new episode below: 